Contributor authorship policy
  Choupo records contributors by name in this file, by copyright lines in
  source files they create or substantially extend, by DCO Signed-off-by
  trailers, and by the git commit author history. Contributions are not
  assigned to Vítor Geraldes or TalentGround Lda.; contributors keep their
  copyright and license their work under GPL-3.0-or-later. The guides/manuals
  are authored and curated by Vítor Geraldes and Pedro Mendes -- except the
  Developer Guide, authored by Vítor Geraldes alone; external contributions do
  not create guide authorship.
